{"tid":1609221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入一入黎幫手","createTime":"2019-10-01T13:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T23:28:32.000Z","uid":325483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"766e86a6d2c32d8630fe47ab7dab91ae5d177cd6","tid":1609221,"uid":325483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"知唔知有冇tg group有醫療資助？ <br />\n我朋友今日去深水埗行街 <br />\n行得太前比班防暴狗打左幾棍<br />\n無耐之後又有催淚煙 食左幾粒 無耐之後頂唔順送左院<br />\n岩岩照完X光照到肋骨對上有個位裂裂地<br />\n要做手術  想搵啲group幫下佢手集資 <br />\n因為佢屋企唔係話好有錢 都盡量籌緊<br />\n有既請聯絡我 <a href=\"https://t.me/ivanjai10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fivanjai10&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=86df0a4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ivanjai10</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw屌你老母臭系死黑警 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcJqm2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcJqm2f.png&h=38a7d2c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAwCXAJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAwCXAJ.png&h=aebc9cc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7973f6681e86dde01052c738f5a1831a1c2d6ab","tid":1609221,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:00:10.000Z","msg":"經過今日 殺警都唔係問題 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fff225e50e1538b50f2fb27c899491fe1b4e456d","tid":1609221,"uid":325483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gL0Vpi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gL0Vpi.png&h=9eb950e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ei5POKs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fei5POKs.png&h=4ca64680&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2cfb27f76751ca05802749bc25